# Handoff bundles regenerate via `npm run handoff:all` (the spec in
# src/data/handoff/<slug>.mjs is the committed source of truth). Manifests +
# whole-page captures are build artifacts; keep only the browsable, curated
# design-intent docs (public/handoff/<slug>/claude/*.md).
public/handoff/**
!public/handoff/**/
!public/handoff/**/claude/*.md

# Client-sensitive material (proposals, pricing, contacts) — NEVER committed;
# these repos and their deployed sites are public.
/docs/private/
